title: A problem about pre-trained model loading.
body:
Hi, the pre-trained model "DANet101_better_model_paddle1.6" can not be loaded successfully in dygraph mode.
```python
import paddle.fluid as fluid
path = 'DANet_models/DANet101_better_model_paddle1.6'
with fluid.dygraph.guard():
    state_dict = fluid.load_dygraph(path)
    print(state_dict)
```
meet the error 
>_pickle.UnpicklingError: invalid load key, '\x02'.

Environments:
python3.6.10
paddlepaddle-gpu 1.8.3.post107

title: 紧急求助！请问您是否使用了Resnet预训练模型？
body: 您好，非常感谢您的项目，但是我有个疑问。您写了动态图版本的程序，一般我们会再训练时使用resnet当预训练模型，但是我在网上没有找到resnet的动态图预训练模型。请问您在训练的时候，是怎么处理的？还是说您这边有预训练模型，方便给个下载链接吗？
